{# Terms-and-conditions fine-print block. Marked clearly as fictional.
   Selected by `noise.tc_block` (one of TC_BLOCKS) or skipped entirely.
   Brand-neutral wording so the same partial serves the Vela Air, Conex Rail,
   and Vela Coach templates. #}
<div class="tc-block">
    <div class="tc-title">Terms &amp; Conditions ({{ tc_block }})</div>
    <p>
        FICTIONAL: This document is part of a synthetic test corpus and does not
        represent a real booking. The carrier shown is a fictional brand created
        for PDF-extraction evaluation. No real fare rules apply.
    </p>
    {% if tc_block == "fare-rules" %}
    <p>
        Tickets are non-transferable. Changes incur a fictional EUR 35 service
        charge per passenger per leg. Refunds processed within an imaginary
        14 business days.
    </p>
    {% elif tc_block == "baggage-policy" %}
    <p>
        One personal item (40 x 25 x 20 cm) included. Cabin baggage up to 8 kg.
        Checked luggage allowances vary by fare class. Fictional values; consult
        the booking confirmation for real numbers.
    </p>
    {% elif tc_block == "covid-advisory" %}
    <p>
        Travelers are responsible for verifying entry requirements at destination.
        A flexible-fare option is recommended for itineraries subject to change.
        (Synthetic advisory — for corpus testing only.)
    </p>
    {% endif %}
</div>
